reviewText:
Thank You
Sorry it took so long for the review

If you're a hunter or if you know one, you'll think this is funny.  The "Spotlight On Deer" episode alone is worth the price of admission, and when you add in the deer holding the safety meeting, well, as Larry would say, that's funny right there.

If you are a Jeff Foxworthy fan as I am, you look for more enjoyment from his performances than this DVD presents.
Watched it once and gave it to Goodwill.

John
Came in great condition, funny movie. If your a Jeff Foxworthy fan you'll love this movie. If you love hunting you'll find it especially funny.
